# Everything MCP Server Settings
# Use this file to configure the Everything MCP server for Claude Desktop
# This is a test server that demonstrates all MCP protocol features
#
# Format:
# SETTING_NAME=value
#
# Optional Settings:
# -----------------
# CONTAINER_NAME - Name of the Docker container (default: everything-mcp-server)
# DOCKER_IMAGE - Docker image name and tag (default: mcp/everything:latest)
# RESTART_CLAUDE - Whether to restart Claude Desktop if it's running (true/false, default: true)
#
# Examples:
# CONTAINER_NAME=my-everything-server
# DOCKER_IMAGE=mcp/everything:custom
# RESTART_CLAUDE=false
#
# Default settings (uncomment and modify as needed):
# CONTAINER_NAME=everything-mcp-server
# DOCKER_IMAGE=mcp/everything:latest
# RESTART_CLAUDE=true
